      • createNewInstance

        StockQuoteGeneratorInterface createNewInstance(java.lang.String symbol)
        This routine fakes a static method that is capable of creating a new instance of the given class. It will return a stock quote generator interface which watches the given string. How this is done is up to the given class.
        Parameters:
        symbol - This is the symbol that is to be watched.
        Returns:
        A new StockQuoteGeneratorInterface realization will be returned.
